Description: Portable 2D Game and Visual Novel Scripting Runtime
 Suika3 is a portable 2D game and visual novel scripting runtime
 designed for cross-platform deployment across desktop, mobile,
 and legacy systems. It features a lightweight C89-based engine,
 hybrid JIT/AOT scripting, and high portability across Unix-like
 systems including Linux, BSD, and others.
